titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on Resolin Red F3BS components I and II.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S5539-5540)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/5/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1997, the duty on N-(2-((2,6-dicyano-4-methylphenyl)azo)-5-(diethylamino) phenyl)-methanesulfonamide and N-(2-((2,6-dicyano-4-methylphenyl)azo)-5-(di-l-propylamino) phenyl)-methanesulfonamide (Resolin Red F3BS Components I and II).
